com.jpl_347E.bio_sigapp

Class ECGCalibrateDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.jpl_347E.bio_sigapp.ECGCalibrateDialog

  • public class ECGCalibrateDialog
extends Activity
    Author:
    John Allard and Jose Figeuroa This class is an activity that gets called when the user selects the "Calibrate" option from the main menu in the ShimmerDevicesMenu activity. This specific activity is only called when the user is on the ShimmerDevicesMenu for the ECG shimmer, and thus this activity is used to calibrate the connected ECG shimmer
